# Local Experiments and Run Outputs (Raw Trajectories)
# Note: Clean statistical results should be committed, but massive raw logs should be ignored.
# For reproducibility, we keep raw logs out of git history and store them in an external archive, or keep them localized.
artifact/baselines/*_raw.jsonl
artifact/decapod-runs/*_raw.jsonl
*.log
*.trace

